page.title: 20CONTRIBUTORS TO THE SURVEY
page.content:
The survey of this D_block was carried out by Farnborough Sixth Form College in June and July 1985. The contributors were teachers and students of the 'Your Locality' general studies course. Your Domesday surveyors were:
Mark Dickinson John Porter Julia Freeman Caroline Riley Rachel Grant Paul Rutty James Knight Simon Whitaker Claire Lynch Darren Williams Ann Paddon Jamie Willis
We hope you have enjoyed reading about our D_block. Further information about it can be found from the 'count data.'
